<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="force-vt">force <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /fɔːs/    美 /fɔːrs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>强迫；迫使：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They didn't force me — I wanted to go.
他们没有强迫我，是我想去的。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>force sb / oneself to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was forced to take a taxi because the last bus had left.
最后一班公交车走了，我只好乘坐出租车了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On cold winter mornings I have to force myself to get up.
在寒冷的冬日早晨，我不得不逼迫自己起床。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>force sb into (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Young people are being forced into earning money before finishing their education.
年轻人被迫在完成学业之前出去赚钱。</p><footer>2015 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>强行；强加：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>force one's way in / out
强行闯入/挤出</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He forced a smile. 
他强颜欢笑。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>forced /'fɔːst/ adj <br />
forceful  /'fɔːsfl/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>forceful personality / character</strong>
很强的个性</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a forceful speech 
有说服力的演讲</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I tell my mom that if we're forced eat things,we may become ill.  （2020全国 改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. eat前加to  </p></div>